description: Ella Reese and Mason Lear are two demanding people who need a subordinate that they can count on. Both of them think they've found exactly what they need in Bentley Layne, the soft-spoken new intern in their office, but neither can decide who his real boss is. Ella and Mason both compete to stake their claim in the tattooed cutie, sweetening the pot for him by offering their tight pussy and hard cock respectively. Soon the pair of high-powered executives have to admit that there's enough of Bentley to go around and the three hotties throw down in a hot and heavy bisexual three-way. Talk about solution oriented problem-solving!
title: Office Politics
